The coefficient of determination was 

A. 0.444
B. 0.556
C. 1.799
D. 2.716

To find the coefficient of determination, we use the formula:

\[ R^2 = 1 - \frac{SS_{\text{residual}}}{SS_{\text{total}}} \]
